{"tid":448150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[累人累物] 廢老「遞遞手」過馬路 途中跌倒險被輾爆頭","createTime":"2017-10-26T03:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T03:05:46.000Z","uid":2547,"like":405,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"a784e86ef002bd0b4f8d3982b7200e2ba87b5548","tid":448150,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VRcROK_5L-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVRcROK_5L-U&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0Xiu26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f3d5b96c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VRcROK_5L-U</a><br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，無論有沒有交通燈，都應該小心注意路面情況。今日網上流傳一段短片，見到一名老婦，在沒有交通燈的馬路中，「遞遞手」就過路，一輛私家車司機讓路，但該名老婦未有注意對頭車，而且對頭車車速很快，老婦欲加速過路，怎料跌到，險被對頭私家車輾爆頭，十分驚險。<br />\n<br />\n網民看過片段後紛批評老婦亂過馬路十分危險，「對頭白色車車速咁高，佢諗住跑得贏架車？好彩佢跌倒，白色車又避到，如果唔係，佢一技(枝)箭直衝，一定撞到應一應」、「最尾果刻以為會車到個頭」。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60928742abaca8b4e71f354a5858f45b7dec8326","tid":448150,"uid":6752,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"趕住去死"},{"pid":"3280d9ac2612ebbd133d788c55dea62ead84683c","tid":448150,"uid":39381,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"佢都算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bff30412f93768eb076a63aba8b4213b019b9c","tid":448150,"uid":61864,"like":340,"dislike":1,"score":339,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:17:48.000Z","msg":"婆婆， 你要自尋短見我唔會阻住你， 呢個係你嘅權利。<br />\n但係你唔好累咗個司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個司機好慘"},{"pid":"8c7954d18fd4a624dd75a09588f1e21499c1e701","tid":448150,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"ci